wdi2-SH.DYN.2024.def: Probability of dying between age 20-24 years of age expressed per 1,000 youths age 20, if subject to age-specific mortality rates of the specified year.
wdi2-SH.DYN.2024.name: Probability of dying among youth ages 20-24 years
wdi2-SH.DYN.2024.source: Estimates developed by the UN Inter-agency Group for Child Mortality Estimation (UNICEF, WHO, World Bank, UN DESA Population Division) at www.childmortality.org.
